We'll continue with the promotional plan.

270
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:44,480
Let's keep going.

271
00:19:44,559 --> 00:19:46,078
When this is over,

272
00:19:46,079 --> 00:19:47,558
I'll pay...

273
00:19:47,559 --> 00:19:49,518
to send everyone on a team-building trip abroad.

274
00:19:49,519 --> 00:19:51,890
- Okay? - Yes!

275
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:54,759
(Box office sales of "Blue Galaxy" continue to rise)

276
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:07,960
Ms. Jiang.

277
00:20:08,359 --> 00:20:09,889
Why did the box office sales go up instead of down?

278
00:20:09,890 --> 00:20:11,239
What are you doing?

279
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:13,599
Things were going according to our plan.

280
00:20:13,650 --> 00:20:15,518
But who knew that Ye Fei Mo and Wen Xiao Nuan...

281
00:20:15,519 --> 00:20:16,960
would suddenly announce their relationship?

282
00:20:17,359 --> 00:20:19,480
Wen Xiao Nuan's sincerity has won the hearts of the netizens.

283
00:20:19,890 --> 00:20:20,890
You're useless.

284
00:20:22,359 --> 00:20:23,410
(Xiao Tian)

285
00:20:27,359 --> 00:20:29,410
- Ms. Jiang. - What is Jiang Fang doing now?

286
00:20:29,799 --> 00:20:31,559
Mr. Jiang is having a meeting with the executives...

287
00:20:31,759 --> 00:20:34,000
to discuss the next step of promoting "Blue Galaxy".

288
00:20:34,170 --> 00:20:35,170
What?

289
00:20:38,599 --> 00:20:41,038
"Blue Galaxy" is doing well now. It's a good opportunity.

290
00:20:41,039 --> 00:20:44,240
Aurora Film can do post-publicity work...

291
00:20:44,279 --> 00:20:45,650
to raise awareness.

292
00:20:47,170 --> 00:20:49,599
I completely agree with Mr. Jiang.

293
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:52,359
I'll supervise the Theater department.

294
00:20:52,759 --> 00:20:53,759
Okay.

295
00:20:53,890 --> 00:20:55,039
Does anyone have anything to add?

296
00:21:00,519 --> 00:21:02,000
Jiang Fang, I have something to say.

297
00:21:02,519 --> 00:21:04,649
Ling Er, I'm in a meeting.
Wait for me in the office, okay?

298
00:21:04,650 --> 00:21:05,920
I want to say it here.

299
00:21:09,170 --> 00:21:11,000
Mr. Jiang, we'll get going then.

300
00:21:34,079 --> 00:21:35,079
What's the matter?

301
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:38,599
Why are you so concerned about "Blue Galaxy"?

302
00:21:40,079 --> 00:21:43,199
"Blue Galaxy" is a theatrical release of Aurora Film.

303
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,518
As the company executive,

304
00:21:44,519 --> 00:21:46,650
what's wrong with being concerned about it?

305
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:49,170
I'm afraid you're concerned about the person in the movie.

306
00:21:50,680 --> 00:21:51,960
Jiang Ling Er, what are you trying to say?

307
00:21:52,559 --> 00:21:54,160
Don't take me for a fool.

308
00:21:54,559 --> 00:21:56,000
Anyone can see it.

309
00:21:56,119 --> 00:21:57,720
You care about "Blue Galaxy"...

310
00:21:57,920 --> 00:21:59,440
because of Wen Xiao Nuan.

311
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:02,879
It was you who announced...

312
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:04,480
Wen Xiao Nuan and Ye Fei Mo's relationship, right?

313
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,759
Yes, it was me.

314
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,799
I want to ruin Wen Xiao Nuan's reputation.

315
00:22:09,119 --> 00:22:10,599
I want you to give up on her.

316
00:22:10,640 --> 00:22:12,199
You're being unreasonable.

317
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,559
I'm being unreasonable?

318
00:22:13,759 --> 00:22:15,199
If you think Wen Xiao Nuan is good,

319
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,200
then go to her.

320
00:22:17,319 --> 00:22:19,240
She's with Ye Fei Mo now.

321
00:22:19,839 --> 00:22:21,960
I'm afraid she has long forgotten about you.

322
00:22:23,519 --> 00:22:24,919
Jiang Ling Er, don't go too far!

323
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:27,160
Jiang Fang, how dare you yell at me?

324
00:22:28,319 --> 00:22:29,559
I'm afraid you've forgotten.

325
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:32,319
Everything you have now was given to you by me.

326
00:22:32,599 --> 00:22:34,078
I worked hard...

327
00:22:34,079 --> 00:22:35,640
for everything I have now!

328
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,440
Worked hard?

329
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:40,160
Without me,

330
00:22:40,759 --> 00:22:42,240
my brother wouldn't even glance at you...

331
00:22:42,599 --> 00:22:44,000
or have given you your current position.

332
00:22:47,599 --> 00:22:49,079
I'm afraid you've forgotten.

333
00:22:49,720 --> 00:22:52,720
Back then, in order to woo me, the daughter of the Jiang family,

334
00:22:53,599 --> 00:22:55,358
you tried so hard to flatter me.

335
00:22:55,359 --> 00:22:56,359
They're fighting.

336
00:22:56,799 --> 00:22:57,838
Be quiet.

337
00:22:57,839 --> 00:22:58,839
Let me tell you.

338
00:22:58,880 --> 00:22:59,880
Listen.

339
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:01,720
Ms. Jiang is so mad.

340
00:23:02,039 --> 00:23:04,959
Mr. Jiang must be having an affair.

341
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:05,960
No way.

342
00:23:05,961 --> 00:23:06,999
My goodness.

343
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:08,880
That's shocking.

344
00:23:13,319 --> 00:23:14,319
Jiang Fang, you can't leave.

345
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:17,200
Jiang Fang.

346
00:23:17,359 --> 00:23:18,838
If you dare to step out of this door today,

347
00:23:18,839 --> 00:23:20,119
I'll ruin your reputation.

348
00:23:31,119 --> 00:23:32,439
She's not a meddler.

349
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,479
(Wen Xiao Nuan and Ye Fei Mo announce relationship)

350
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:34,480
She's the one I love.

351
00:23:52,559 --> 00:23:54,319
The situation has changed.

352
00:23:55,759 --> 00:23:58,519
Many people were moved by Wen Xiao Nuan's honesty.

353
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:01,039
The box office sales of "Blue Galaxy" has bounced back.

354
00:24:02,519 --> 00:24:04,240
Han Hui, what should we do?

355
00:24:11,039 --> 00:24:12,599
Contact the screenwriter, Mr. Liu.

356
00:24:12,799 --> 00:24:14,960
Ask him to come to the studio tonight.

357
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:16,680
Okay.

358
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:27,960
(Big Princess)

359
00:24:31,519 --> 00:24:32,519
What is it, Mom?

360
00:24:33,799 --> 00:24:36,319
Can't I call you if there's nothing?

361
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,839
You've forgotten about me now that you have a wife.

362
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:42,079
I saw the news.

363
00:24:42,200 --> 00:24:43,919
Bring Nuan Nuan home for dinner tomorrow.

364
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:44,920
I want to see her.

365
00:24:45,559 --> 00:24:46,960
It's not like you haven't seen her before.

366
00:24:47,119 --> 00:24:49,440
She's the daughter-in-law of the Ye family now.

367
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:51,759
Of course I have to meet her formally.

368
00:24:51,839 --> 00:24:53,079
It's etiquette.

369
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:55,640
I'll wait for you at home tomorrow.

370
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:57,960
Okay.

371
00:25:09,119 --> 00:25:14,720
Two, three, four, five, six, seven.

372
00:25:15,279 --> 00:25:16,319
Coming.

373
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:22,119
Why are you here?

374
00:25:23,839 --> 00:25:25,200
My mom wants to see you tomorrow.

375
00:25:26,599 --> 00:25:27,758
She said...

376
00:25:27,759 --> 00:25:30,480
she wants you to meet her formally as her daughter-in-law.

377
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,798
Then should I bring a gift...

378
00:25:33,799 --> 00:25:35,279
for the first official meeting?

379
00:25:36,119 --> 00:25:37,278
Don't worry about the gift.

380
00:25:37,279 --> 00:25:38,318
I'll ask Maggie to buy it...

381
00:25:38,319 --> 00:25:39,319
and deliver it tomorrow morning.

382
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:41,440
No, I have to prepare it myself.

383
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:45,839
My mom loves perfume.

384
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:47,559
Why don't you give her a bottle of perfume?

385
00:25:52,559 --> 00:25:54,679
Thank you for coming to the studio, Mr. Liu.

386
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:55,680
Don't mention it.

387
00:25:56,680 --> 00:26:00,720
It's an honor to have dinner with you, Ms. Han.

388
00:26:02,279 --> 00:26:04,559
I've always been a fan of you.

389
00:26:04,799 --> 00:26:07,039
In all the characters I've created,

390
00:26:07,279 --> 00:26:08,960
there are traces of you in them.

391
00:26:09,799 --> 00:26:11,959
No wonder every time I read your work,

392
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,400
I can relate to them so deeply.

393
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:15,640
It's not just that the script is good.

394
00:26:15,839 --> 00:26:17,960
I could also see myself in it.

395
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:20,999
The story you told me the last time we met,

396
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:23,039
I've turned it into a movie script.

397
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:25,880
It's called "Twin Flowers".

398
00:26:26,279 --> 00:26:27,839
I'm sure you'll like it.

399
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:34,439
I'll read it carefully then.

400
00:26:34,440 --> 00:26:35,440
Of course.

401
00:26:35,799 --> 00:26:38,119
It's my honor. Cheers.

402
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:47,440
Okay.

403
00:26:51,079 --> 00:26:52,480
(Ling Er)

404
00:26:55,799 --> 00:26:56,799
Come in.

405
00:26:57,759 --> 00:26:58,759
Mr. Jiang.

406
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:03,118
This is the latest attendance rate and box office ratings...

407
00:27:03,119 --> 00:27:04,759
of "Blue Galaxy" and "Magpie Bridge".

408
00:27:05,759 --> 00:27:07,960
Currently, all major box office evaluators believe...

409
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:10,758
that the single-day ticket sales of our two films...

410
00:27:10,759 --> 00:27:11,799
still have room for growth.

411
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,200
Not bad.

412
00:27:15,519 --> 00:27:17,159
Both projects were secured by you.

413
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:18,518
Aurora Film's vice president position...

414
00:27:18,519 --> 00:27:19,880
is yours for sure this time.

415
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:24,160
(Jiang Hao)

416
00:27:24,799 --> 00:27:28,799
Mr. Jiang probably wants to praise you after seeing the reports.

417
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:31,359
You can go now.

418
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:40,160
Mr. Jiang.

419
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:41,400
Jiang Fang.

420
00:27:41,799 --> 00:27:43,799
I just saw the company's report.

421
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:47,519
Your projects "Blue Galaxy" and "Magpie Bridge" did very well.

422
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:48,920
Congratulations.

423
00:27:48,921 --> 00:27:50,200
It's all thanks to you, Mr. Jiang.

424
00:27:50,559 --> 00:27:52,079
It's all thanks to Ling Er's good taste.

425
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:54,079
She chose you to be the general manager.

426
00:27:54,319 --> 00:27:55,599
That's why you're here today.

427
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:58,920
Yes, Mr. Jiang.

428
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,680
My little sister grew up under my care.

429
00:28:02,079 --> 00:28:03,400
Although she's willful,

430
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:05,559
she's devoted to you.

431
00:28:06,359 --> 00:28:07,680
She even reminded me yesterday...

432
00:28:07,839 --> 00:28:09,680
that you're working hard for the company.

433
00:28:09,839 --> 00:28:10,839
You're always working overtime.

434
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:11,880
She feels bad for you.

435
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:12,960
She asked me to promote you.

436
00:28:13,359 --> 00:28:15,279
Everyone knows how capable you are.

437
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:17,239
Ling Er supports you a lot.

438
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:19,440
As a big brother, I feel sorry for my sister.

439
00:28:19,599 --> 00:28:21,160
So I'll support you all the way.

440
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:23,720
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

441
00:28:44,839 --> 00:28:47,319
Mr. Jiang, please call me back when you're available.

442
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:54,359
Hello.

443
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:55,680
Ms. Han.

444
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:57,599
I've got a weapon in my hand...

445
00:28:58,039 --> 00:29:00,960
that can separate Wen Xiao Nuan and Ye Fei Mo forever.
